Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.45,0:22:03.07,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)\an8}水面に浮かんでいる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.40,0:22:05.53,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)\an8}木の葉のように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.54,0:22:10.30,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)\an8}僕ら行先も知れず
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.37,0:22:14.51,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)\an8}流され 戦ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.71,0:22:17.66,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)\an8}離れ離れになって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.68,0:22:20.26,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)\an8}空っぽになっても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.27,0:22:22.54,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)\an8}また背負い込んで行く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.61,0:22:26.74,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)\an8}去っていったあなたの想いが
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.76,0:22:30.06,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)\an8}僕を支えてる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.28,0:22:35.70,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)\an8}追い続けたら見える新世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.91,0:22:39.56,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)\an8}限界だなんて幻想だろう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.65,0:22:43.19,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)\an8}Yeah upside down, upside down
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.24,0:22:46.58,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}覆してやろう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.12,0:22:51.56,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}奪われようと 失くしてはいない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.74,0:22:55.56,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}胸の中で生きていれば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.67,0:22:59.24,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}Yeah upside down, upside down
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.24,0:23:04.09,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}この居場所を終わらせない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.45,0:22:03.07,EDCNcht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}我們如同落葉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.40,0:22:05.53,EDCNcht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}飄零於水面上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.54,0:22:10.30,EDCNcht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}漂泊不知去處
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.37,0:22:14.51,EDCNcht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}隨波逐流而戰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.71,0:22:17.66,EDCNcht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}即便天涯兩隔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.68,0:22:20.26,EDCNcht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}即便身無一物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.27,0:22:22.54,EDCNcht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}只得背負一切
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.61,0:22:26.74,EDCNcht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}念你如初
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.76,0:22:30.06,EDCNcht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}前行不止
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.28,0:22:35.70,EDCNcht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}不斷追尋 新世界就在前方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.91,0:22:39.56,EDCNcht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}極限云云 不過是幻想而已
Comment: 0,0:22:39.65,0:22:43.19,EDCNcht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}Yeah upside down, upside down
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.24,0:22:46.58,EDCNcht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}將一切反轉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.12,0:22:51.56,EDCNcht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}即便被奪走也不會失去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.74,0:22:55.56,EDCNcht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}只要你還活在我的心中
Comment: 0,0:22:55.67,0:22:59.24,EDCNcht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}Yeah upside down, upside down
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.24,0:23:04.09,EDCNcht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}我就不會容許這片土地淪陷
