Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.50,0:00:43.46,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}問いかけたまま
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.75,0:00:49.63,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}答えはもう届かなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.59,0:00:57.85,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}溢れた感情を失くさないで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.89,0:01:03.90,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}心があれば守り抜けるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.90,0:01:09.99,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}命の音が聞こえるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.99,0:01:15.99,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}心の中 きみがいるから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.99,0:01:18.29,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}We will remember your name
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.29,0:01:20.58,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}We will remember your dream
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.58,0:01:22.21,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}Remember you're braver
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.21,0:01:24.38,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}We will remember your name
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.38,0:01:26.71,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}We will remember your dream
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.71,0:01:28.84,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}Remember you're braver
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.13,0:01:33.55,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}朱く焼けた世界を闇が青に染めて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.26,0:01:36.26,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}この目で見た
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.26,0:01:38.64,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}その目に焼き付いた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.81,0:01:40.98,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}Remember you're braver
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.14,0:01:43.77,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}遥かなる道を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.06,0:01:47.23,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}積み重なる悲しみを
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.40,0:01:51.20,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}きみと生きよう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.24,0:01:56.03,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}僅かな望みを
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.28,0:01:59.29,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}答えのないその問いを
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.29,0:02:00.91,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}もう一度
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.04,0:02:04.92,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}もう二度と
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.50,0:00:43.46,OPCNcht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}叩問內心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.75,0:00:49.63,OPCNcht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}終究沒有得到答案
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.59,0:00:57.85,OPCNcht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}不要忘記曾經滿腔的熱忱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.89,0:01:03.90,OPCNcht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}只要本心尚存便能守護至終
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.90,0:01:09.99,OPCNcht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}聽見生命的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.99,0:01:15.99,OPCNcht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}只因為心中有你
